WEBVTT

00:09:28.750 --> 00:09:30.390
muloqot bunga ta'sir ko'rsatadi.

00:09:30.390 --> 00:09:33.377
Keyin esa maktabga 
qatnay boshlaymiz

00:09:33.377 --> 00:09:35.298
va muammo yana bittaga ko'payadi.

00:09:35.298 --> 00:09:36.442
Menga maktablar yoqadi,

00:09:36.442 --> 00:09:41.529
lekin o'qituvchilar 
eskirgan dunyoqarashni o'rgatadi.

00:09:41.529 --> 00:09:44.130
Ular maktabga qatnagan paytida bilim oldi

00:09:44.130 --> 00:09:46.683
va endi dunyo haqidagi shu bilimlarini

00:09:46.683 --> 00:09:48.889
o'quvchilarga beg'araz o'rgatishadi.

00:09:48.889 --> 00:09:51.118
Nashr etilgan kitoblar, 
shubhasiz, eskirgan,

00:09:51.118 --> 00:09:54.049
axir dunyo doimiy o'zgarishda.

00:09:54.049 --> 00:09:55.296
O'quv materiallarini

00:09:55.296 --> 00:09:58.545
yangilab turish o'ta mushkul.

00:09:58.545 --> 00:10:00.529
Mana biz nimaga e'tibor qaratyapmiz.